  {
    "type": "EXPOSITORY (ENGLISH BIBLE)",
    "name": "Jamieson-Fausset-Brown Bible Commentary",
    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "14. fruit of your doings—(Pr 1:31; Isa 3:10, 11).",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "forest thereof—namely of your city, taken from Jer 21:13. \"Forest\" refers to the dense mass of houses built of cedar, &c., brought from Lebanon (Jer 22:7; 52:13; 2Ki 25:9).   ",
        "children": []
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "type": "EXPOSITORY (ENGLISH BIBLE)",
